9}, {\"ngram\": \"sport and performance art\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"so synchronised swimming\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythmic gymnastics\", \"from\": 3575, \"to\": 3594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What we are going to see is the very, very best breakers in the entire world.\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the very, very best breakers\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3653}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire world\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, that sense of competition is still there.\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that sense\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Olympics has never stayed the same.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Time and time and time again, it has shifted and changed, moved with the times and responded to culture to attract new audiences.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the times\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"new audiences\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just see the addition of breaking as a furtherance of that narrative.\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the addition\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3916}, {\"ngram\": \"a furtherance\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"that narrative\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Yes, there are other sport-arts they could have chosen here, of course, but I think the Olympic committee has decided to go with breaking because it 